            <p>Mike Manna-- A Professional Inside & Outside the Ring, plus Cutman Eddie Holiday--Both men in the sport for the right reasons!<span id="dots"></span><span id="more">&nbsp; &nbsp;I spent time in the gym with Mike Manna and pro cutman Eddie Holiday as Mike trains for the headline event with Andrew Satterfield on August 7th in Moundsville, WV.  We covered Mike's reasons for donating his purse to charitable causes, how he maintains two professional careers: Insurance and Professional Boxing. Plus, Cutman Eddie Holiday corners pro boxers for the right reasons.  Don't miss this interview!</span></p>
            <button onclick="myFunction()" id="myBtn">Read more</button>
